        // ‚úÖ ‡∏ü‡∏±‡∏á‡∏Å‡πå‡∏ä‡∏±‡∏ô‡πÄ‡∏•‡∏∑‡∏≠‡∏Å‡∏Ñ‡∏≥‡∏ö‡∏£‡∏£‡∏¢‡∏≤‡∏¢
        document.querySelectorAll(".subtitle-selector").forEach((selector, index) => {
